com.percussion.services.publisher
Interface IPSDeliveryType

All Superinterfaces:
IPSCatalogIdentifier, IPSCatalogItem, Serializable
public interface IPSDeliveryType
extends IPSCatalogItem

A delivery location has the representation for a single publisher plugin. The delivery location determines what spring bean is looked up in the publisher and dictates whether an item needs to be assembled for unpublishing.
